_tags.description: Japetić is the highest peak of Plešivica, a reserve of forest vegetation with preserved natural beauty. It is a perfect place for hiking, cycling, mountain climbing and nature lovers in general. At the top there is a beautiful view of the region.
_tags.name: Japetić
Kislica
_tags.note: On some paper maps this peak is named Špičasti vrh, but local community uses name Kislica. Špičasti vrh is eastern (lower) peak

Špičasti vrh
